{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id914a2380-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9689"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"9689"},"text":"§ 9689.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Reference","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"With respect to any function transferred under this subchapter (including under a reorganization plan under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s9682"},"text":"section 9682 of this title","children":[],"tail":") and exercised on or after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2018-10-05"},"text":"October 5, 2018","children":[],"tail":", reference in any other Federal law to any department, commission, or agency or any officer or office the functions of which are so transferred shall be deemed to refer to the Corporation or official or component of the Corporation to which that function is so transferred."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id914a2381-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/254/dF/tVI/s1469"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–254, div. F, title VI, § 1469","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2018-10-05"},"text":"Oct. 5, 2018","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/132/3515"},"text":"132 Stat. 3515","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id914a2382-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id914a2383-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id914a2384-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This subchapter, referred to in text, was in the original “this title”, meaning title VI (§§ 1461–1470) of div. F of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/254"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–254","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2018-10-05"},"text":"Oct. 5, 2018","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/132/3510"},"text":"132 Stat. 3510","children":[],"tail":", which is classified principally to this subchapter and which repealed title IV of chapter 2 of part I of the Foreign Assistance Act of 1961 ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s2191"},"text":"22 U.S.C. 2191","children":[],"tail":" et seq.), other than subsections (g), ("},{"tag":"i","attrib":{},"text":"l","children":[],"tail":"), (m), and (n) of section 237 thereof ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s2197/g"},"text":"22 U.S.C. 2197(g)","children":[],"tail":", ("},{"tag":"i","attrib":{},"text":"l","children":[],"tail":"), (m), (n)), among other amendments. For complete classification of title VI to the Code, see Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
